raw_data.title: Developer
raw_data.description: The Developer is responsible for programming, data modeling, and product enhancement. Programming responsibilities include planning, building, testing, debugging and performing related activities within prescribed timelines and with the required software and hardware technology. Data modeling experience includes all activities related to the analysis of system requirements, development of accurate models and graphical representations of system needs and business processes and implementing or adjusting that model in the given database system according to client needs and/or recommendations resulting from internal process review. Product enhancement responsibilities include the research, planning, building, testing, and debugging which is intended to change or improve the functionality, performance, usability or other quality of Social Solutions’ systems, software, databases, data, or other system component.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: Can be substituted for six (6) years of relevant experience.
